## Outcomes & Impact

Systems inspired by these modules delivered measurable improvements:

• 5% improvement in sell-through rate  
• 7% increase in availability of top-selling SKUs  
• 5-day reduction in inventory holding cover  
• 8% reduction in ageing inventory  
• 593 man-hours saved annually through automation


## Product Lessons

Inventory optimisation requires tightly coupled decision systems rather than isolated tools.

Data quality and demand forecasting accuracy are critical foundations for automated decision making.

Human override mechanisms remain essential in complex retail environments where qualitative insights complement algorithmic recommendations.
